      "timestamp": "2026-05-28T13:11:00Z",
      "error_message": "npm install in whatsapp_bridge fails: 'Failed to set up chrome v146! ... All providers failed: read ECONNRESET' (Puppeteer postinstall Chromium download), exit code 1; rollback then hits EPERM rmdir on node_modules.",
      "file": "whatsapp_bridge/index.js, whatsapp_bridge/package.json",
      "root_cause": "whatsapp-web.js depends on puppeteer, whose postinstall downloads a ~150MB Chromium. The download was killed by a flaky network (ECONNRESET) and the whole install failed.",
      "fix": "Install with PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD=true (bash) / $env:PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD='true' (PowerShell), then drive the system browser: index.js auto-detects Chrome/Edge (or CHROME_PATH) and passes it as puppeteer.executablePath. Verified: bridge launches Chrome and renders the linked-device QR.",
